,"count":1},{"word":"absolutely","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"I feared as much. Then this is where we... stop.","quest_name":"Flames of Heart","quest_id":121000038},{"text":"Strange. I remember everything about Septimont, but... I can't remember... I can't even remember my name.","quest_name":"Flames of Heart","quest_id":121000038},{"text":"Too bad I won't last long enough to see that happen.","quest_name":"Flames of Heart","quest_id":121000038},{"text":"I'm sorry, Cartethyia. You saved me, but I can't help you in return.","quest_name":"Flames of Heart","quest_id":121000038},{"text":"That's right... my city is beautiful.","quest_name":"Flames of Heart","quest_id":121000038},{"text":"When the autumn wind blew through the golden flags and wind chimes, time seemed to slow...","quest_name":"Flames of Heart","quest_id":121000038},{"text":"Septimont... can I leave it to you?","quest_name":"Flames of Heart","quest_id":121000038},{"text":"You mean...","quest_name":"Flames of Heart","quest_id":121000038},{"text":"Must be quite the person, eh? I wish I could meet {Male=him;Female=her}... and see how {Male=he;Female=she} does it...","quest_name":"Flames of Heart","quest_id":121000038},{"text":"Alright, Cartethyia... I'll... I'll try my best...","quest_name":"Flames of Heart","quest_id":121000038},{"text":"First... tell me, what is that person's name?","quest_name":"Flames of Heart","quest_id":121000038},{"text":"I'm managing. I-I can still move, but I'm exhausted. I've walked for so long, for so far... but I still can't leave this city.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"The white <te href=850161>Tidal Blight</te> follows me wherever I go.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"I… don't remember.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"Who… are you?","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"A wandering knight… ah.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"Thank you for your help these past few days.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000126},{"text":"The Tidal Blight is spreading faster. I'm afraid—","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000126},{"text":"The mastermind behind this will be tricky to deal with.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000126},{"text":"You really trust {Male=him;Female=her}, don't you?","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000126},{"text":"Absolutely.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000126}]}